We all have to deal with that.

00:18:06.570 --> 00:18:08.910
And so this number,
what we're hoping

00:18:08.910 --> 00:18:12.060
to do is give you some data
that can help you drive

00:18:12.060 --> 00:18:14.870
that decision, give
you some information

00:18:14.870 --> 00:18:17.610
that can help you
make those decisions

00:18:17.610 --> 00:18:19.350
on a day to day basis.

00:18:19.350 --> 00:18:22.005
But quality is
absolutely important.

00:18:25.810 --> 00:18:30.830
This is another kind of
quality/basics type of thing.

00:18:30.830 --> 00:18:35.540
Apps designed for tablets
monetize 10 times better than

00:18:35.540 --> 00:18:37.390
those that aren't.

00:18:37.390 --> 00:18:40.300
When you have someone
using a device,

00:18:40.300 --> 00:18:43.860
they expect the app
to work well in it.

00:18:43.860 --> 00:18:47.260
They expect it to be
designed for that device.

00:18:47.260 --> 00:18:49.340
If you are not designed
for that device,

00:18:49.340 --> 00:18:51.670
then don't target that
device, but if you

00:18:51.670 --> 00:18:53.650
are trying to
acquire users, again,

00:18:53.650 --> 00:18:57.570
tablet users or
specific device users,

00:18:57.570 --> 00:19:00.190
then you have to build
an application that

00:19:00.190 --> 00:19:03.550
works well and is
designed for that device.

00:19:03.550 --> 00:19:06.540
This is really, really
important, especially

00:19:06.540 --> 00:19:11.240
as we see more form factors
become available on Android.

00:19:11.240 --> 00:19:15.560
Whether it's Auto, ATV,
Android TV, or Wear.

00:19:20.360 --> 00:19:22.620
So Wear, you get
it almost for free,

00:19:22.620 --> 00:19:26.780
but you should check whether
the basic experience works well.

00:19:26.780 --> 00:19:29.650
Of course, you can build really,
really awesome experiences

00:19:29.650 --> 00:19:34.240
when you tailor your app's
experience for that ecosystem,

00:19:34.240 --> 00:19:38.710
but the baseline is make sure
that whatever device tier

00:19:38.710 --> 00:19:42.560
you're targeting, that
it's designed for it

00:19:42.560 --> 00:19:44.007
and it works well in it.

00:19:44.007 --> 00:19:46.090
There's going to be more
and more of these things,

00:19:46.090 --> 00:19:47.960
so you really need
to say ahead of it.

