plus buying markets,

00:20:05.770 --> 00:20:08.067
and so that gives
you lots of choices.

00:20:08.067 --> 00:20:10.150
It gives you a lot of
countries you can target to.

00:20:10.150 --> 00:20:11.691
It gives you a lot
of countries where

00:20:11.691 --> 00:20:13.500
