00:20:13.500 --> 00:20:17.760
But be very mindful of what
countries you're targeting.

00:20:17.760 --> 00:20:20.490
Be very purposeful.

00:20:20.490 --> 00:20:24.580
When you reach a market, design
your app for that device.

00:20:24.580 --> 00:20:25.980
Localize your listing.

00:20:25.980 --> 00:20:27.820
Localize your pricing.

00:20:27.820 --> 00:20:30.310
If you're acquiring
users in a market,

00:20:30.310 --> 00:20:34.270
just be very
intentional about it.

00:20:34.270 --> 00:20:36.770
Being easily global
on this platform

00:20:36.770 --> 00:20:40.610
has that double edged sword of
one, you reach a billion users.

00:20:40.610 --> 00:20:43.340
On the other side, you
reach a billion users,

00:20:43.340 --> 00:20:46.990
and so you need to think about,
