00:20:46.990 --> 00:20:49.040
interact with your
app, and make sure

00:20:49.040 --> 00:20:52.150
that your experience is good.

00:20:52.150 --> 00:20:55.280
That's the second point around
localize, localize, localize.

00:20:55.280 --> 00:20:59.090
And finally, continue
to focus on quality.

00:20:59.090 --> 00:21:02.940
We on Google Play are extremely,
extremely focused on quality

00:21:02.940 --> 00:21:04.540
and make sure that
our users have

00:21:04.540 --> 00:21:07.220
a great experience on Android.

00:21:07.220 --> 00:21:11.810
And so success is directly tied
to you building great quality

00:21:11.810 --> 00:21:12.910
apps.

00:21:12.910 --> 00:21:17.510
This is especially true, again,
as the proliferation of devices

00:21:17.510 --> 00:21:19.760
